snippet.title: Sigh.. Some People Need Our Attention & 🎅🏼 Christmas Wishlist's 🎄
snippet.description:
#WishLists #TisTheSeason #Amazon
#TheTruth #RepAsh #Grinches
Wendy, Randi and Stephanie on panel with me 
Some people are grinches. Some people don't know what sarcasm is.. Some people are full of it.  Rep Ash grow up.  The Truth get a funny bone or at least know what you're talking about  Mind your own business!! One last thing.. Get rid of the doxxers holding wrenches in this community and doxxing all together ..Transcending Obsession.. The name alone is funny 
🎅🏼 We are going to help these kids  🎄
👕👚SWAG 🎽☕
